[&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_ol]:pl-[1.7em] text-ds-purple-900 group-[.theme-set]/theme:text-ds-primary [&amp;_a]:text-ds-purple-500 [&amp;_a:hover]:text-ds-purple-700 [&amp;_a:hover]:underline group-[.theme-set]/theme:[&amp;_a]:text-ds-brand font-kraken-product text-[16px] font-normal leading-[22px]"><p>Below you can find four sections with detailed information on Kraken&#x27;s linear multi-collateral perpetual and fixed maturity derivatives contracts. <br/></p><p>Click to expand each section: </p></div></div><div class="pt-8 lg:pt-10 !w-screen !max-w-full"><div class="[&amp;_div[id^=&#x27;content-&#x27;]]:!overflow-y-auto [&amp;_div[id^=&#x27;content-&#x27;]]:!ease-out [&amp;_div[id^=&#x27;content-&#x27;]]:!duration-200 [&amp;_button[aria-controls^=&#x27;content-&#x27;]]:!max-w-[min(var(--article-max-width),calc(100vw-calc(2*var(--article-content-x-padding))))] [&amp;_button[aria-controls^=&#x27;content-&#x27;]]:!left-1/2 [&amp;_button[aria-controls^=&#x27;content-&#x27;]]:!-translate-x-1/2 [&amp;_button[aria-controls^=&#x27;content-&#x27;]]:!relative"><div class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0"><div class="relative"><button id="85bl7ei4pfcn0gwysz59" type="button" aria-controls="content-85bl7ei4pfcn0gwysz59" aria-expanded="false" class="bg-ds-accordion focus-visible:rounded-ds-2 focus:outline-ds-accordion outline-offset-ds-accordion w-full cursor-pointer border-0 py-0 text-left focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 disabled:cursor-not-allowed pl-0 hover:bg-ds-accordion-hover group"><div class="py-ds-5 flex w-full items-center shadow-ds-accordion"><div class="text-ds-body1 text-ds-accordion-primary group-hover:text-ds-accordion-hover" data-testid="title">Perpetual Contract Specifications</div><div class="pl-ds-7 ml-auto flex flex-shrink-0 items-center" data-testid="chevron-down"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 w-ds-icon-md h-ds-icon-md" name="ChevronDownSmall"><path d="M7.5 9.98291L11.2045 13.6874C11.6438 14.1268 12.3562 14.1268 12.7955 13.6874L16.5 9.98291" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="fill-transparent stroke-ds-icon-dimmed"></path></svg></div></div></button><div id="content-85bl7ei4pfcn0gwysz59" aria-labelledby="85bl7ei4pfcn0gwysz59" data-testid="content-85bl7ei4pfcn0gwysz59" style="display:block" class="transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out overflow-hidden max-h-0 opacity-[0]"><div class="pb-4"><div class="space-y-6 pb-8 pt-2 [&amp;&gt;:not(:has(table))]:mx-auto [&amp;&gt;:not(:has(table))]:w-full [&amp;&gt;:not(:has(table))]:max-w-[var(--article-max-width)]"><div class="[&amp;_a:hover]:font-inherit [&amp;_a:hover]:underline [&amp;_a]:no-underline [&amp;_blockquote]:pl-ds-6 [&amp;_blockquote]:text-ds-body1 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:bg-ds-dimmed [&amp;_blockquote]:before:w-ds-2 [&amp;_blockquote]:relative [&amp;_blockquote]:before:absolute [&amp;_blockquote]:before:-inset-y-0 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:left-0 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:content-[&quot;&quot;] [&amp;_em]:italic [&amp;_h1]:text-[2em] [&amp;_h2]:text-[1.55em] [&amp;_h3]:text-[1.33em] [&amp;_h4]:text-[1.11em] [&amp;_h5]:font-medium [&amp;_h6]:font-medium [&amp;_*:not(span)+*:not(span)]:mt-[1em] [&amp;_p+ol]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_p+ul]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li]:break-words [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:pl-[1.5em] [&amp;_ol&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol&gt;li::marker]:font-bold [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_ol]:pl-[1.7em] text-ds-purple-900 group-[.theme-set]/theme:text-ds-primary [&amp;_a]:text-ds-purple-500 [&amp;_a:hover]:text-ds-purple-700 [&amp;_a:hover]:underline group-[.theme-set]/theme:[&amp;_a]:text-ds-brand font-kraken-product text-[16px] font-normal leading-[22px]"><p>Perpetual Derivatives are a type of Derivatives contract that have <strong>no expiration date</strong> and an <strong>auto-rolling</strong> feature <strong>every hour</strong>. </p><p>Perpetual contracts feature a funding rate, a payment between traders designed to keep the contract&#x27;s price aligned with the underlying asset&#x27;s spot price. More information on this mechanism can be found under &quot;Perpetual Contract Funding Rate Information&quot; in the next drop-down menu. </p><p><strong>Margin Class</strong> and maximum leverage by position size are detailed in <a target="blank" href="/articles/360022632452-derivatives-margin-schedule-maximum-leverage">Derivatives Margin Schedule &amp; Maximum Leverage</a>.</p><p><br/>Forex Perpetual (FX perps) information is detailed in <a target="blank" href="/articles/forex-perpetual-futures">Forex Perpetual Futures</a></p></div><div class="box-border w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out max-h-80"><div data-testid="notification-container" aria-labelledby=":R1999l9d6:" aria-describedby=":R1999l9d6H1:" class="relative flex min-w-[300px] items-start overflow-hidden backdrop-blur-xl bg-ds-notification-primary rounded-ds-notification-md p-ds-4 md:items-center text-ds-notification-primary ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 group gap-ds-notification-non-stacked-md"><div class="ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0 rounded-ds-round flex size-fit p-ds-circle-md bg-ds-circle-primary text-ds-circle-primary" data-testid="leading-icon"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="size-ds-circle-icon-md ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0" name="InfoCircle"><path d="M11 11H12V16M21 12C21 16.9706 16.9706 21 12 21C7.02944 21 3 16.9706 3 12C3 7.02944 7.02944 3 12 3C16.9706 3 21 7.02944 21 12Z" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="fill-transparent stroke-current"></path><rect x="11.5" y="7.5" width="1" height="1" rx="0.5" stroke-width="2" class="fill-current stroke-current"></rect></svg></div><div class="flex flex-1 flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-ds-notification-non-stacked-md"><div class="flex flex-col"><span id=":R1999l9d6:" class="text-ds-notification-title-md">Please note:</span><span id=":R1999l9d6H1:" class="text-ds-notification-text-md text-ds-notification-subtitle-primary"><div class="[&amp;_em]:italic hover:[&amp;_a]:text-ds-textlink-hover-primary [&amp;_a]:text-ds-notification-subtitle-primary"><p></p><p>Delisted and settled contracts are archived <a href="/articles/7526425887508-Futures-contracts-trading-suspensions-delistings">here</a>. </p><p></p></div></span></div></div></div></div><div class="relative overflow-x-auto"><table class="mobile-table w-full text-left"><thead class="border-b border-solid border-ds-grey-700 min-h-[undefinedpx]"><tr class="border-b border-solid border-ds-grey-700"><th class="py-ds-5 pr-ds-10 overflow-hidden text-ellipsis min-w-[148px] text-ds-primary align-top sticky top-0"><span class="text-ds-primary text-ds-label1 ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0"><p><strong>Symbol</strong></p></span></th><th class="py-ds-5 pr-ds-10 overflow-hidden text-ellipsis min-w-[148px] text-ds-primary align-top sticky top-0"><span class="text-ds-primary text-ds-label1 ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0"><p><strong>Base Currency</strong></p></span></th><th class="py-ds-5 pr-ds-10 overflow-hidden text-ellipsis min-w-[148px] text-ds-primary align-top sticky top-0"><span class="text-ds-primary text-ds-label1 ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0"><p><strong>Min Lot</strong></p></span></th><th class="py-ds-5 pr-ds-10 overflow-hidden text-ellipsis min-w-[148px] text-ds-primary align-top sticky top-0"><span class="text-ds-primary text-ds-label1 ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0"><p><strong>Tick Size</strong></p></span></th><th class="py-ds-5 pr-ds-10 overflow-hidden text-ellipsis min-w-[148px] text-ds-primary align-top sticky top-0"><span class="text-ds-primary text-ds-label1 ms-ds-0 me-ds-0 mt-ds-0 mb-ds-0"