t-[.75em] [&amp;_p+ul]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li]:break-words [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:pl-[1.5em] [&amp;_ol&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol&gt;li::marker]:font-bold [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_ol]:pl-[1.7em] text-ds-purple-900 group-[.theme-set]/theme:text-ds-primary [&amp;_a]:text-ds-purple-500 [&amp;_a:hover]:text-ds-purple-700 [&amp;_a:hover]:underline group-[.theme-set]/theme:[&amp;_a]:text-ds-brand font-kraken-product text-[16px] font-normal leading-[22px]"><p>The Impact Mid is the median of the average entry price market-selling x value of contracts and market-buying x value of contracts. </p><p>The contract values for Impact Mid are regularly updated. </p><p>For current contract-specific Impact Mid values see our API&#x27;s <a target="blank" href="https://futures.kraken.com/derivatives/api/v3/instruments">Instruments Endpoint</a>. </p></div></div></div><div class="pt-8 lg:pt-10"><div id="article-block-e63dc5d9a447" style="--header-height:0px" class="space-y-2 scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+5rem)] lg:scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+2rem)]"><h4 class="[&amp;_a:hover]:font-inherit [&amp;_a:hover]:underline [&amp;_a]:no-underline [&amp;_blockquote]:pl-ds-6 [&amp;_blockquote]:text-ds-body1 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:bg-ds-dimmed [&amp;_blockquote]:before:w-ds-2 [&amp;_blockquote]:relative [&amp;_blockquote]:before:absolute [&amp;_blockquote]:before:-inset-y-0 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:left-0 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:content-[&quot;&quot;] [&amp;_em]:italic [&amp;_h1]:text-[2em] [&amp;_h2]:text-[1.55em] [&amp;_h3]:text-[1.33em] [&amp;_h4]:text-[1.11em] [&amp;_h5]:font-medium [&amp;_h6]:font-medium [&amp;_*:not(span)+*:not(span)]:mt-[1em] [&amp;_p+ol]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_p+ul]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li]:break-words [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:pl-[1.5em] [&amp;_ol&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol&gt;li::marker]:font-bold [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_ol]:pl-[1.7em] text-ds-purple-900 group-[.theme-set]/theme:text-ds-primary [&amp;_a]:text-ds-purple-500 [&amp;_a:hover]:text-ds-purple-700 [&amp;_a:hover]:underline group-[.theme-set]/theme:[&amp;_a]:text-ds-brand font-kraken-product text-[16px] font-medium leading-[22px] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+5rem)] lg:scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+2rem)]"> Global Platform Max Order Size </h4><div class="[&amp;_a:hover]:font-inherit [&amp;_a:hover]:underline [&amp;_a]:no-underline [&amp;_blockquote]:pl-ds-6 [&amp;_blockquote]:text-ds-body1 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:bg-ds-dimmed [&amp;_blockquote]:before:w-ds-2 [&amp;_blockquote]:relative [&amp;_blockquote]:before:absolute [&amp;_blockquote]:before:-inset-y-0 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:left-0 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:content-[&quot;&quot;] [&amp;_em]:italic [&amp;_h1]:text-[2em] [&amp;_h2]:text-[1.55em] [&amp;_h3]:text-[1.33em] [&amp;_h4]:text-[1.11em] [&amp;_h5]:font-medium [&amp;_h6]:font-medium [&amp;_*:not(span)+*:not(span)]:mt-[1em] [&amp;_p+ol]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_p+ul]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li]:break-words [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:pl-[1.5em] [&amp;_ol&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol&gt;li::marker]:font-bold [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_ol]:pl-[1.7em] text-ds-purple-900 group-[.theme-set]/theme:text-ds-primary [&amp;_a]:text-ds-purple-500 [&amp;_a:hover]:text-ds-purple-700 [&amp;_a:hover]:underline group-[.theme-set]/theme:[&amp;_a]:text-ds-brand font-kraken-product text-[16px] font-normal leading-[22px]"><p>The maximum individual order size is $20,000,000 for all contracts and order types. A single order placed with a USD value higher than this amount will not execute. </p></div></div></div><div class="pt-8 lg:pt-10"><div id="article-block-fb2fad2a663a" style="--header-height:0px" class="space-y-2 scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+5rem)] lg:scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+2rem)]"><h4 class="[&amp;_a:hover]:font-inherit [&amp;_a:hover]:underline [&amp;_a]:no-underline [&amp;_blockquote]:pl-ds-6 [&amp;_blockquote]:text-ds-body1 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:bg-ds-dimmed [&amp;_blockquote]:before:w-ds-2 [&amp;_blockquote]:relative [&amp;_blockquote]:before:absolute [&amp;_blockquote]:before:-inset-y-0 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:left-0 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:content-[&quot;&quot;] [&amp;_em]:italic [&amp;_h1]:text-[2em] [&amp;_h2]:text-[1.55em] [&amp;_h3]:text-[1.33em] [&amp;_h4]:text-[1.11em] [&amp;_h5]:font-medium [&amp;_h6]:font-medium [&amp;_*:not(span)+*:not(span)]:mt-[1em] [&amp;_p+ol]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_p+ul]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ol+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+p]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ol]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul+ul]:mt-[1.25em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ul&gt;li]:break-words [&amp;_ul]:list-disc [&amp;_ul]:pl-[1.5em] [&amp;_ol&gt;li+li]:mt-[.75em] [&amp;_ol&gt;li::marker]:font-bold [&amp;_ol]:list-decimal [&amp;_ol]:pl-[1.7em] text-ds-purple-900 group-[.theme-set]/theme:text-ds-primary [&amp;_a]:text-ds-purple-500 [&amp;_a:hover]:text-ds-purple-700 [&amp;_a:hover]:underline group-[.theme-set]/theme:[&amp;_a]:text-ds-brand font-kraken-product text-[16px] font-medium leading-[22px] scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+5rem)] lg:scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+2rem)]"> Decimal &amp;amp; Thousands Separator Formatting </h4><div class="[&amp;_a:hover]:font-inherit [&amp;_a:hover]:underline [&amp;_a]:no-underline [&amp;_blockquote]:pl-ds-6 [&amp;_blockquote]:text-ds-body1 [&amp;_blockquote]:before:bg-ds-dimmed [&amp;_blockquote]:before:w-ds-2 [