me":"Support","field_selfservice":{"field_articles_postfix":"articles"},"field_signinout":[{"_key":"874829daf8c5","_type":"menuItem","field_event_placement":"Sign in","field_url":"https://www.kraken.com/sign-in","title":"Log in"},{"_key":"029d032e5e28","_type":"menuItem","field_event_placement":"Sign up","field_url":"{{ \"https://kraken.onl/JDNW\" if isMobile else \"https://www.kraken.com/sign-up\" }}","smart_link_mode":"enabled","title":"Sign up"}],"lastPublishedAt":"2025-06-10T21:46:39.839Z","score":2},"data":{"_createdAt":"2025-04-02T06:52:32Z","_id":"article-4844359082772","_rev":"IISvBCAl0vvMpcXtmQ6OiE","_type":"page","_updatedAt":"2025-05-26T15:33:53Z","appId":"support","field_page_components":[{"_key":"295a203a6ebc","_type":"paragraphArticleLayout","field_children":[{"_key":"f5adb07b4a52","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp\u003eBelow you can find four sections with detailed information on Kraken\u0026#x27;s linear multi-collateral perpetual and fixed maturity derivatives contracts. \u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eClick to expand each section: \u003c/p\u003e"},{"_key":"7d533f2badf1","_type":"paragraphAccordion","field_children":[{"_key":"4b668ca2b1f0","_type":"paragraphAccordionItem","field_children":[{"_key":"b4eb252ed041","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyLc","field_body":"\u003cp\u003ePerpetual Derivatives are a type of Derivatives contract that have \u003cstrong\u003eno expiration date\u003c/strong\u003e and an \u003cstrong\u003eauto-rolling\u003c/strong\u003e feature \u003cstrong\u003eevery hour\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePerpetual contracts feature a funding rate, a payment between traders designed to keep the contract\u0026#x27;s price aligned with the underlying asset\u0026#x27;s spot price. More information on this mechanism can be found under \u0026quot;Perpetual Contract Funding Rate Information\u0026quot; in the next drop-down menu. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMargin Class\u003c/strong\u003e and maximum leverage by position size are detailed in \u003ca href=\"/articles/360022632452-derivatives-margin-schedule-maximum-leverage\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eDerivatives Margin Schedule \u0026amp; Maximum Leverage\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eForex Perpetual (FX perps) information is detailed in \u003ca href=\"/articles/forex-perpetual-futures\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\"\u003eForex Perpetual Futures\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"_key":"d979cd789449","_type":"paragraphNotification","field_alternative_icon":"InfoCircle","field_can_be_closed":false,"field_direction":"inline","field_has_icon":true,"field_text":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cp\u003eDelisted and settled contracts are archived \u003ca href=\"/articles/7526425887508-Futures-contracts-trading-suspensions-delistings\" \u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","field_title":"Please note:","field_tone":"primary"},{"_key":"39ef46ef64b1","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTable","field_rows":[{"_key":"6fac65be6530","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableRow","field_cells":[{"_key":"b77b51d92f96","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column :: Symbol","field_content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSymbol\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"_key":"937fb7c85872","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column :: Base Currency","field_content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBase Currency\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"_key":"d9f617854a29","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column :: Min Lot","field_content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMin Lot\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"_key":"5f847fecb27a","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Column :: Tick Size","field_content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTick Size\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"_key":"8caf7ab94d81","_type":"paragraphArticleBodyTableCell","cell_description":"Colum