Cookie Settings","config_support][f56d3d7ebc5c][title":"Recruitment Privacy Notice","config_support][4c2e637ead02][title":"Recruitment Privacy Notice","config_support][bc0c8d169bcf][title":"Disclosures","config_support][903b0ed761f4][title":"Disclosures","config_support][46b09f152b9f][title":"Exchange Trading Rules","config_support][field_copyrightnotice][field_privacy_statement":"© 2011 - {YYYY} Payward, Inc.","config_support][field_country_banner_text":"You're viewing the website for {{ appCountry.description }}, but it looks like you're in {{ userCountry.description }}. Do you want to switch countries?","config_support][field_country_label":"Country","config_support][802e3e205e50][field_body":"\u003cp\u003eKraken provides services in France through its company Coin Meester B.V., registered with the Autorit\u0026eacute; des March\u0026eacute;s Financiers (AMF) as a digital asset service providers (DASP) with Registration Number E2022-058.\u003c/p\u003e\n","config_support][26bff10ff9f1][field_body":"\u003cp\u003eIn connection with the cooperation between Kraken and DLT Finance, this service is provided by DLT Finance, a brand of DLT Securities GmbH and DLT Custody GmbH. BaFin supervises DLT Securities GmbH for crypto trading and DLT Custody GmbH for crypto custody.\u003c/p\u003e\n","config_support][de3d81413f8d][field_body":"\u003cp\u003eThis page is for Kraken Global. Please visit \u003ca href=\"https://blog.kraken.com/japan\"\u003eblog.kraken.com/japan\u003c/a\u003e for information on services, documents and notices for customers residing in Japan.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"columns\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"column\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eImportant notice about crypto asset trading\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eCrypto assets are not a national currency in or outside of Japan. Because the price of crypto assets can fluctuate, there is a possibility of loss. If the private keys are lost, you may completely lose access to the corresponding crypto assets and their value may be lost.\u0026nbsp;Breakdowns in the blockchain transfer mechanism could cause crypto assets to lose their value. Crypto assets can be used to pay for goods only when the seller has consented to accepting crypto assets as consideration.\u0026nbsp;When trading crypto assets, please understand the transaction details completely and proceed at your own discretion.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"column\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eImportant notice about Staking service\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Staking service is a loan transaction of crypto assets based on a crypto asset loan for consumption agreement. This does NOT mean that clients perform staking on their own. Crypto assets borrowed by us are not subject to segregation management since this activity does not fall under a Crypto Asset Exchange activity under the Payment Services Law. This service is not covered by deposit insurance. Reward rates\u0026nbsp; (Usage Fee on the\u0026nbsp; Loan for Consumption Agreement) reflect the annual percentage rate (APR). All reward rates are estimates subject to change. When using the Staking service, please understand the transaction details completely by reading \u0026ldquo;Terms and Conditions of Crypto Asset Loan for Consumption Agreement\u0026rdquo; and \u0026ldquo;Transaction Manual for Crypto Asset Loan for Consumption Agreement\u0026rdquo;, and proceed at your own discretion.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n","config_support][9ad373f8affb][field_body":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cem data-stringify-type=\"italic\"\u003eThese materials are for general information purposes only and are not investment or financial product advice or a recommendation or solicitation to buy, sell, stake or hold any cryptoasset or to engage in any specific trading strategy. Kraken does not and will not work to increase or decrease the price of any particular cryptoasset it makes available. The unpredictable nature of the crypto-asset markets can lead to loss of funds. Tax may be payable on any return and/or on any increase in the value of your cryptoassets and you should seek independent advice on your taxation position. Geographic restrictions may apply. Some crypto products and markets are unregulated. Kraken\u0026rsquo;s regulatory status for its various products and services differs per jurisdiction and you may not be protected by government compensation and/or regulatory protection schemes. See Legal Disclosures for each jurisdiction (\u003ca href=\"/legal/disclosures\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e).\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","config_support][eb9feede74d8][field_body":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePayward Canada Inc., operating as Kraken, has filed an application for registration in certain Canadian jurisdictions but has not yet obtained registration. Until such time as Payward Canada Inc., operating as Kraken, obtains registration, Payward Canada Inc. has agreed to abide by the terms of an undertaking available at \u003ca href=\"https://www.securities-administrators.ca/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/20230324-Kraken-PRU-publication-version.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ethis page\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","config_support][9a861241faf9][field_body":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eLa inversi\u0026oacute;n en criptoactivos no est\u0026aacute; regulada, puede no ser adecuada para inversores minoristas y perderse la totalidad del importe invertido. Es importante leer y comprender los riesgos de esta inversi\u0026oacute;n que se explican detalladamente en esta ubicaci\u0026oacute;n. Las rentabilidades pasadas no constituyen un indicador fiable de las rentabilidades futuras.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n","config_support][ba2151f863ee][title":"Margin Trading","config_support][77df40bd22a2][title":"{{\"Derivatives Trading\" if (countryCode | lower)