"linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][f5adb07b4a52][field_body":"\u003cp\u003eBelow you can find four sections with detailed information on Kraken\u0026#x27;s linear multi-collateral perpetual and fixed maturity derivatives contracts. \u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eClick to expand each section: \u003c/p\u003e","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][b4eb252ed041][field_body":"\u003cp\u003ePerpetual Derivatives are a type of Derivatives contract that have \u003cstrong\u003eno expiration date\u003c/strong\u003e and an \u003cstrong\u003eauto-rolling\u003c/strong\u003e feature \u003cstrong\u003eevery hour\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePerpetual contracts feature a funding rate, a payment between traders designed to keep the contract\u0026#x27;s price aligned with the underlying asset\u0026#x27;s spot price. More information on this mechanism can be found under \u0026quot;Perpetual Contract Funding Rate Information\u0026quot; in the next drop-down menu. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMargin Class\u003c/strong\u003e and maximum leverage by position size are detailed in \u003ca href=\"/articles/360022632452-derivatives-margin-schedule-maximum-leverage\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eDerivatives Margin Schedule \u0026amp; Maximum Leverage\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eForex Perpetual (FX perps) information is detailed in \u003ca href=\"/articles/forex-perpetual-futures\" target=\"blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-testid=\"external-link\"\u003eForex Perpetual Futures\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][d979cd789449][field_text":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cp\u003eDelisted and settled contracts are archived \u003ca href=\"/articles/7526425887508-Futures-contracts-trading-suspensions-delistings\" \u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","linear_multi-collateral_derivatives_contract_specifications][d9